column3: Fixed cosmetics and added a change to fail if windres isn't found for win32 build, since it's needed for bitcoind.exe now.\n
Untested ACK, but I prefer if you could fix my nits ;).\n

Nits fixed, last time I hope :)

Uploaded here if you'd like to verify, I have no win32 machine: http://coryfields.com/bitcoind-versioninfo.exe
